          "title": "drop: 0xb10c 27.0rc1 & 25.2rc2 (hash mismatch)",
          "body": "Similar to #1197, this drops my recent SHA256SUMS as they don't match the others. I recently switched to a new GUIX build setup, which I think is the cause for this mismatch.\r\n\r\nAffected are:\r\n\r\n- 27.0 (added #1194; removed #1197)\r\n- 27.0rc1 (added #1169; removed here)\r\n- 25.2rc2 (added #1170; removed here)\r\n\r\nSee also: https://github.com/bitcoin-core/guix.sigs/commits?author=0xB10C",
